    {
      "id": "boundary-root",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🧭 Data vs UI Boundary Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "width": 880,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Data vs UI Boundary Contract\n\nThis contract defines the **hard boundary** between graph data and editor-only state.\n\nIf this boundary blurs, portability and safety collapse.\n\nThis graph is normative.",
