    {
      "id": "boundary-tests",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Boundary Tests",
      "position": {
        "x": -900,
        "y": 420
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Boundary Tests\n\n### Meaning Ownership Test\nIf removing the editor changes interpretation, it is **data**.\n\n### Portability Test\nIf a graph is exported, reloaded, and still works, the data is correct.",
