      "height": 460,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Graph Data Includes\n\n- nodes, edges, clusters\n- ports and semantics\n- schema versions\n- manifest and intent\n- execution-relevant metadata\n\nGraph data is **meaning-bearing** and must survive export.",
