    {
      "id": "diff-hygiene",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Diff Hygiene Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 960
      },
      "width": 880,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Diff Hygiene Rules\n\n- UI state must never appear in diffs\n- Graph diffs must be human-readable\n- Meaning changes must be obvious\n\nIf a diff is confusing, the boundary has been violated.",
